cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI 

The paper deals with 3D scan registration in planetary environments, which involves computer vision and robotics. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.RO (Robotics) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves geometric analysis and feature detection, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper proposes an alternative approach to 3D scan registration, which involves computing descriptors and matching features, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
